  <summary>AI-enhanced, GPU-accelerated (WGPU) terminal emulator</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      OpenAgent Terminal is a modern, AI-enhanced terminal emulator focused on performance and privacy.
      It provides command assistance with a local-first design, while maintaining a fast, GPU-accelerated
      rendering pipeline powered by WGPU.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>AI command assistance (local or cloud, opt-in)</li>
      <li>Wayland and X11 native</li>
      <li>Privacy-first (no telemetry)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

